description: Make your way to Lei Away Ladies for the most heavenly cuisine that Hawaii has to offer, right on the streets of Southern California.  You’ll find a tasty selection of island-inspired items, like Teriyaki & Poke Bowls, Spam Musubi, Maui Wowie Donuts, and so much more. So come on out to this tropical truck and say “Aloha!” to this talented team, and then “Mahalo!” for this delicious luau in your mouth!
name: Lei Away Leidies
